title: 680: BITCOIN TO ‘GO NUTS’ IN NOVEMBER, PREDICTS ON-CHAIN ANALYST WILLY WOO - HERE’S WHY!!!!!
description:
Widely followed on-chain analyst Willy Woo predicts Bitcoin will ‘go nuts’ in the coming months as long-term holders continue to accumulate the leading cryptocurrency (BTC).

“This is a macrocycle thing. You would have seen it at the 2015, 2014 bottom. You saw it at the 2019 bottom, and actually, you saw it over the 2020 where we came back down."
